snippet.title: Official HITMAN™ 2 Elusive Target No. 1 Trailer Staring Sean Bean
snippet.description: Sean Bean stars as Mark Faba in HITMAN 2’s first Elusive Target mission, The Undying. Releasing November 20th, you only have 10 days to take down Faba.
